short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces names of Australian cities with their traditional counterparts

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do you know what lands you live on? You can learn the traditional names of Australian cities by seeing them every day. This extension replaces all instances of specific place names with their traditional counterparts automatically. More names will be added in all updates.
